    <img src="<%= asset_path 'homeImg.png' %>" alt="Home Image" class="mt-1 mb-3 w-100 h-100 d-inline d-md-none"> 
    <div class="container  lh-base text-start">
        <p>Tired of complicated and cluttered applications? Our sleek, easy-to-use interface gives you 
